<i>adjective</i>: 찡하다 [찡하다], 감격스럽다 [감ː격쓰럽따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>찡하다 [찡하다]</dt><br>
<dd>touched; moved</dd><br>
<dd>감동을 받아 가슴이 뻐근하거나 벅찬 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being moved emotionally and feeling a twinge or swell in one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감격스럽다 [감ː격쓰럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>impressed; touched</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 느끼는 감동이 크다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling or being touched by something very deeply.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>